{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805170/extras/AddToWishlist.png?t=1738811776\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Uncover the mystery of the town of Marwood</strong></h2></h2>At the end of the Wild West era, Marcus, a teenager from a noble family, decides to find out why his city suffers from evil dreams. To find the reason, he goes to his neighbors' nightmares, where he may find out the truth or get stuck forever.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2>Evil Dreams - 2D adventure with elements of psychological horror and a variable plot. You have to travel between the real world and the world of the dreamers, find out the hidden secrets of the citizens, try don't lose mind and much more. And fully hand-drawn 2D graphics in the author's style, combined with an immersive soundtrack and a historically correct setting will help you with this.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805170/extras/GifUpperworld.gif?t=1738811776\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A living world filled with colorful characters, interactive environment and references.<br></li><li>Hand-drawn 2D graphics in the author's style.<br></li><li>Lots of puzzles, mechanics, secrets, and Easter eggs will not let you get bored!<br></li><li> Recreated from archival photos of the U.S. at the end of the 19th century.<br></li><li>You influence the development of the story and the fate of Marcus.<br></li><li>Travel between worlds, where you will have to look for clues and remember key places in the nightmare world.<br></li><li>Problems of moral choice and life of Native Americans in the 19th Century.<br></li><li>And much more!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805170/extras/GifPromo1.gif?t=1738811776\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Welcome to Mordox!</stro